Where a `ScheduledSession` has at least one `Offer` with `price` set to `0`, it should also have a property named `isAccessibleForFree` set to `true`.

For example:

```
{
  "@type": "ScheduledSession",
  "offers": [
    {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "price": 0
    }
  ],
  "isAccessibleForFree": true
}
```

Recommended property `image` is missing from `SessionSeries`.

A full example looks like this:

```
"image": [
  {
    "@type": "ImageObject",
    "url": "http://example.com/static/image/speedball_large.jpg",
    "thumbnail": [
      {
        "@type": "ImageObject",
        "url": "http://example.com/static/image/speedball_thumbnail.jpg"
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

